item.description: I am a first year PhD student at the University of Waterloo under joint supervision of Prof. Greg Rice and Prof. Joel Dubin. I am also affiliated with Health Data Science Lab (HDSL). My other personal website hosted by UWaterloo server can be found here. Before arriving to UWaterloo, I obtained MSc and BSc degrees at the University of Victoria in a beautiful city, Victoria, British Columbia, Canada. In my spare time, I like to play basketball, and reading books, articles and random posts in various different genre.
